        "richtext_6W4MDL": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>This konjac was developed by the third-generation owner, Koji, after much trial and error in his quest to create the real thing.<br/>He named it \"Kikumatsu Konjac\" after the founder, Kikumatsu Nakao.</p><p>The first generation founded the company, the second generation expanded it, the third generation refined the manufacturing techniques, and the current fourth generation, who is the representative, is working hard every day to spread the product to the world.We<br/>will continue to make it with care so that it will become a product that will be loved by everyone for a long time to come as our company's signature product.</p>"
